title: Warrior Fighter-PLAZA
description:
The warriors of history fight for immortal  glory.  Warrior  Fighter
  pits the most skilful warriors of all time against each other  in  a
  one on one fighter, combining cinematic presentation with fast-paced
  moves and play. From the imperial palace of Rome to the  streets  of
  the future choose single player mode to  conquer all  eight  of  the
  warriors one at  a time,  or two  player challenger  mode  to  fight
  warrior against warrior.

  For more info go to : http://store.steampowered.com/app/941670/
